content.text: Welcome to my simple web site!

I'm someone who has been learning computer science since 2014. Along the way I have had my interest peaked by CGI, Data Scraping, Web Development, Numerical Computation, and Probability. I'm focused on improving these skills through my current job and personal projects. I love to search for bugs and think of extreme edge cases.
